https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/Suicide-Squad-Kill-The-Justice-League-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/Suicide-Squad-Kill-The-Justice-League-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/Suicide-Squad-Kill-The-Justice-League-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <em><a href="https://www.nme.com/games/suicide-squad-kill-the-justice-league">《自杀小队：杀死正义联盟》</a></em>在抢先体验版推出不到一个小时后， <a href="https://www.nme.com/brands/rocksteady-studios">Rocksteady Studios</a>被迫下线。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/gaming-features/inside-the-lost-gaming-history-of-gorillaz-3478233">从“生化危机”到“WarioWare”：Gorillaz 失落的游戏历史</a></strong></li></ul><p><em>《自杀小队：杀死正义联盟》</em>将于 2 月 2 日通过<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/ps5">PS5</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/xbox-series-xs">Xbox Series X|S</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/brands/steam">Steam</a>发布，但购买更昂贵的豪华版的玩家可以<a href="https://www.nme.com/guides/gaming-guides/suicide-squad-kill-the-justice-league-early-access-3577600">提前 72 小时访问游戏。</a></p><p>该抢先体验窗口已于今天（1 月 29 日）早些时候开放，首先向新西兰玩家开放，但游戏很快因错误而下线。有些玩家在第一次登录时，发现游戏已经自动完成了。</p><p> Rocksteady 在社交媒体上发帖<a href="https://twitter.com/suicidesquadRS/status/1751938662093263232" target="_blank" rel="noopener">写道</a>：“我们意识到许多玩家目前遇到了一个问题，即在第一次登录游戏时，他们已经完成了完整的故事。”</p><p>为了修复该错误，该工作室确认将在<em>《自杀小队：杀死正义联盟</em>》不久后下线，对游戏服务器进行“维护”。 “我们预计这需要几个小时，一旦我们获得更多信息，我们将进行更新。对于给您带来的不便，我们深表歉意。”他们写道。 </p><figure id="attachment_3577810" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3577810" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3577810" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/suicide-squad-kill-the-justice-league-game-pass.jpg" alt="《自杀小队》杀死正义联盟：可以看到死亡射手正在射击敌人" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/suicide-squad-kill-the-justice-league-game-pass.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/suicide-squad-kill-the-justice-league-game-pass-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/suicide-squad-kill-the-justice-league-game-pass-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/suicide-squad-kill-the-justice-league-game-pass-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/suicide-squad-kill-the-justice-league-game-pass-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/suicide-squad-kill-the-justice-league-game-pass-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3577810" class="wp-caption-text">图片来源：Rocksteady Studios</figcaption></figure><p>此前， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/rocksteady-warns-fans-about-disappointing-suicide-squad-kill-the-justice-league-leaks-3560996">开发商警告粉丝避免“令人失望的”叙事泄露</a>。 “我们期待玩家体验我们在<em>《自杀小队：杀死正义联盟》</em>中精心打造的故事。我们希望每个人都能玩游戏，亲身感受故事的每一个时刻。我们只能敦促您尽量避免剧透。”</p><p>本周早些时候，有消息称<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/denuvo-quietly-added-to-suicide-squad-kill-the-justice-league-3578593">Rocksteady 已经悄然在游戏中添加了有争议的反盗版系统 Denuvo。</a></p><p>在其他新闻中， <a href="https://www.nme.com/games/vampire-the-masquerade-bloodlines-2"><em>《吸血鬼：避世血统 2》</em></a>背后的团队谈到了其“ <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/vampire-the-masquerade-bloodlines-2-director-compares-combat-to-dishonored-and-fallout-3578673">沉浸式战斗</a>”系统，该系统受到了<em><a href="https://www.nme.com/games/dishonored">《耻辱》</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/games/fallout">《辐射》</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/games/god-of-war">《战神》</a></em>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/games/elden-ring"><em>《埃尔登指环》</em></a>的影响。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/rocksteady-pulls-suicide-squad-an-hour-into-early-access-over-auto-complete-bug-3578689">Rocksteady 因自动完成错误而将《自杀小队》提前一小时下架的帖子</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
